body:
Addressed inline comments

- reused debugName (changing it to prettyName)
- Py_RETURN_NONE
- THPUtils_packString
- public api is "name"
- don't ever throw exceptions/errors. duplicate names are now allowed

I intend to separately add a test in https://github.com/ezyang/onnx-pytorch/blob/master/test/test_models.py

After offline discussion with @houseroad, I intend to send a separate PR with naming of inputs/outports specifically for the export() function.
